      <p/>
      <p>A <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">shadow</a> can be difficult to see in dark or gloomy areas but stands out starkly in brightly illuminated places.<a href="img/MonstersS.Shadow.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersS.Shadow.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">shadow</a> is 5 to 6 feet tall and is weightless. <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">Shadows</a> cannot speak intelligibly.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
